General.Name: Global Service Center Public Company Limited
General.Description: Global Service Center Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides customer support and debt collection services in Thailand. The company offers call center, telemarketing, and tele sales services using phone, computer network, and other telecommunication systems. It also engages in the real estate business; hemp-cannabis and related business; and platform and software business. Global Service Center Public Company Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.
